data.title: ‘Clerks III’ Interview with Kevin Smith, Jason Mewes
data.meta_description: "Clerks III" stars Kevin Smith, Jason Mewes, Brian O'Halloran, Jeff Anderson and Trevor Fehrman chat about the third "Clerks" movie in this interview with CinemaBlend's Jeff McCobb at San Diego Comic-Con. They chat about everything from View Askew’s history to Jason Mewes’ dream of becoming a wax figure.
data.text:
"Clerks III" stars Kevin Smith, Jason Mewes, Brian O'Halloran, Jeff Anderson and Trevor Fehrman chat about the third "Clerks" movie in this interview with CinemaBlend's Jeff McCobb at San Diego Comic-Con. They chat about everything from View Askew’s history to Jason Mewes’ dream of becoming a wax figure.
